data.label: ShareSDK
data.description: ShareSDK 是全球最流行的应用和手机游戏社交 SDK !到目前为止，我们已经支持了几十万名客户。 ShareSDK 可以轻松支持世界上40多个社交平台的第三方登录、分享和与好友列表操作。短短几个小时，这个小程序包将使您的应用程序完全社会化! 想在中国社交平台上发布你的应用吗？这可能是你最好的选择!

data.label: ShareSDK
data.description: ShareSDK is the world's most popular social SDK for apps and mobile games! So far, we have supported hundreds of thousands of customers. ShareSDK can easily support third-party login, sharing, and friend list operations on more than 40 social platforms worldwide. In just a few hours, this small package will fully socialize your application! Want to release your app on Chinese social platforms? This might be your best choice!
